{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a **Shopify section (Liquid)** for a clean blog introduction area for a luxury perfume brand.
    
    Section purpose:
    This section appears at the **top of the blog page** and introduces the blog category (like "Lifestyle").
    
    Design requirements:
    
    * Minimal and elegant layout
    * Content must start aligned with the **blog grid/images below**
    * Left-aligned content
    * Heading on top
    * Small paragraph text under the heading
    * Large white space around the content
    * Maximum text width **600–700px**
    * Section aligned toward the **left side of the page**
    * Clean luxury design similar to **modern perfume brand websites**
    
    Typography:
    
    * Heading: bold, large font size (around 40–44px)
    * Paragraph: smaller text, **light grey color**
    * Comfortable spacing between heading and paragraph
    * Elegant spacing above and below the section
    
    Section settings (Shopify schema):
    Add editable settings in the **theme editor** for:
    
    1. Heading text
    2. Description text
    3. Layout width option
    
    Width options required:
    
    * **Boxed**
    * **Container**
    * **Full Width**
    * **Custom Width**
    
    Behavior:
    
    * **Boxed** → centered layout with limited width
    * **Container** → use the theme's default container width (same alignment as blog grid)
    * **Full Width** → section spans entire page width
    * **Custom Width** → allow user to define custom max-width in pixels
    
    Additional requirement:
    
    * The text must start from the **same horizontal alignment as the blog images/posts below**.
    * The inner content width should be limited to **600–700px** for better readability.
    
    Code requirements:
    
    * apply full **Shopify Liquid + HTML + CSS**
    * Include **complete section schema**
    * Use clean semantic HTML
    * Ensure responsive layout
    * Follow Shopify best practices
    * Keep the code optimized and easy to maintain
    
    Default content:
    
    Heading:
    Lifestyle
    
    Paragraph:
    Discover fragrance stories, perfume guides, and inspiration from the world of scent. Explore tips on choosing the perfect perfume, understanding fragrance notes, and finding your signature scent.
    
    last time i created with same script description font was not working
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% liquid
  assign container_class = ''
  if block.settings.layout_width == 'boxed'
    assign container_class = 'ai-blog-intro-boxed-' | append: ai_gen_id
  elsif block.settings.layout_width == 'container'
    assign container_class = 'ai-blog-intro-container-' | append: ai_gen_id
  elsif block.settings.layout_width == 'full'
    assign container_class = 'ai-blog-intro-full-' | append: ai_gen_id
  elsif block.settings.layout_width == 'custom'
    assign container_class = 'ai-blog-intro-custom-' | append: ai_gen_id
  endif
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-blog-intro-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.spacing_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.spacing_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-boxed-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 30px;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ settings.container }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ settings.gutter }}px;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-full-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 {{ settings.gutter }}px;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-custom-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.custom_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ settings.gutter }}px;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.content_max_width }}px;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.spacing_between }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.heading_transform }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.heading_letter_spacing }}em;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.description_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: {{ block.settings.description_line_height }};
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.description_letter_spacing }}em;
  }

  .ai-blog-intro-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-blog-intro-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.spacing_top_mobile }}px 0 {{ block.settings.spacing_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-blog-intro-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size_mobile }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.spacing_between_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-blog-intro-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-blog-intro-boxed-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-blog-intro-container-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-blog-intro-full-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-blog-intro-custom-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-blog-intro-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="{{ container_class }}">
    <div class="ai-blog-intro-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
        <h1 class="ai-blog-intro-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.heading }}
        </h1>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
        <div class="ai-blog-intro-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.description }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

